2 CONC efore Mark decided to marry Cleopatra, and thus legitimize their children in 40 B.C.
2 CONT Mark Anthony then married (3) Octavia (then a widow), sister of Octavian, Julius Caesar's heir. This marriage took place as Cleopatra was giving birth to his last child, Ptolemy Philedephus, in 36 B.C. 
